<Speech gate:gateId="64874" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="64758" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="64523" majorType="speaker">ΣΠΥΡΙΔΩΝ-ΑΔΩΝΙΣ ΓΕΩΡΓΙΑΔΗΣ</Parlmember>:</SpeechStart> Ναι, το γνωρίζω. 
